Oppa!

4
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,290
This is nuts.

5
00:00:28,350 --> 00:00:29,740
Woohoo!

6
00:00:29,750 --> 00:00:30,740
Woohoo!

7
00:00:30,750 --> 00:00:33,540
Will your gaze meet mine?

8
00:00:33,550 --> 00:00:36,660
My heart bounce, bounces

9
00:00:36,670 --> 00:00:38,600
I fear it might just jump right out from me

10
00:00:38,610 --> 00:00:40,100
Woohoo!

11
00:01:02,670 --> 00:01:03,960
Sintong, Bangtong,

12
